Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.59,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,The silver pin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生(かりう)）クラスの男女 成績１位が\N着けることができる—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.84,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,given to the boy and girl in each class \Nwith the top test scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シルバーピン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.60,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Tuition exemption. Commute allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学費免除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交通費支給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.60,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Free lunch at the school cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学食無料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:14.52,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I never cared about those perks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そんな特典は\Nどうでもよくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.31,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,It proved you were top of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:19.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラス内１位の証 委員長の証
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:18.94,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,That you were class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.48,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,That's the kind of status\Nthe pin conferred upon you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうステータスとして—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.40,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,and I was proud of myself when I wore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:24.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしは それを着けている自分が\N誇りだった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:27.25,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Kariu, committee meeting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:26.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神(おおが)）狩生！ 委員会 行こ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.12,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\Nそれに あたしにとっては…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:29.96,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:31.78,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.08,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Going to the cafeteria now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:36.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）今から学食？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）うわっ！\Nおっ おっ 大神！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.08,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,O-Oga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.04,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, but I'm waiting for Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:43.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほのかを待ってて\N大神は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.39,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:46.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 委員長の仕事か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.03,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Oh, class rep work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:50.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）\Nそう 俺も腹ペコなのにさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:47.90,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.22,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,And I'm starving, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく 先生\N人使い荒くて まいっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:53.28,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Sensei really runs us ragged!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:54.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ？ 日代(ひしろ)さん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:54.93,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Right, Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）カズ君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）そこの廊下に\N了(りょう)のノートが落ちてましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:17.05,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Ryo's notebook was lying \Non the floor in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）あ… ああ…\N（大神）えっ？ 了って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:17.71,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:19.00,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Who's Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.83,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kazu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:22.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）大丈夫ですか？ カズ君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:24.18,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Sorry, it got a bit heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん ちょっと重くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:26.38,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,This is why I told you\Nto let me carry half.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:26.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）だから\N手伝うと言ったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）すいません
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:27.51,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:33.01,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Give that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）貸してください\N半分 持ちますから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:34.69,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I'll take half.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:37.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）あっ 了って\N夜明(よあけ)君のことだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:37.39,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Oh, "Ryo" is Yoake-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲いいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:38.43,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,You friends with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:40.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）了は 去年\N同じクラスだっただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:40.87,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,He was just in the same class last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.61,Main Dialogue Top,Oga,0,0,0,,So... first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）で 名前呼び？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なの!?\N今の勝ち誇ったような顔！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:45.61,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,What was with that victorious smirk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なの!?\N今の勝ち誇ったような顔！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.83,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,She was trying for a friendly smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎(かいざき)）あの子\Nあれで 愛想笑いのつもりなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\Nあれの どこが 愛想笑いよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.53,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,What part of that was "friendly"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.74,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,She was sneering at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:55.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人をバカにして！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.32,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来(たまらい)）どうしたの？\Nなんか 怒ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.28,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Are you mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:42.95,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:42.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.37,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Argh, I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:47.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ああ イライラする！\Nあの顔が 頭から離れない！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.62,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I can't get that face out of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:50.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）にへー…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.70,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why's she flashing that gross face at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で ゲス顔\Nキラキラさせてんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味分かんない！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.12,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玲奈(れな) やっぱり イライラしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.83,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Rena, you're definitely pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.42,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for your fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャーハン かわいそう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}White Milk\NNon-homogenized
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.30,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,You lack calcium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カルシウム 取りな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.09,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Want some milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:03:59.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牛乳 飲む？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.17,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく ご飯に\N牛乳なんて飲むよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.55,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,How do you drink milk with rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？ 普通じゃん 給食とか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.39,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Huh? It's normal! \NAll through grade school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ 給食は\N出されたから飲んでたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.47,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,They didn't give us an option back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）私は バレーのために\N牛乳 飲みまくって—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:15.73,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drink a ton of milk \Nand grow taller for volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと 身長伸ばすんだ ふふっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）完全に—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.48,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,All that nutrition...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.99,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...is going somewhere else entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:22.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部 違う所に\N栄養 行ってる気がするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:32.41,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Honoka wound up beating me \Non every part of the fitness test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 体力テストは 全部\Nほのかに かなわなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.79,Flashback Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,I knew it! You're really fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）\Nあっ やっぱり すごい速い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）お名前は すみません\N分からないので呼べませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.17,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,As for your name, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.42,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I don't know it, so I couldn't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.63,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Honoka... and Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ほのかも 日代も—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.55,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who sees us as rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしだけが\Nライバル視していて—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:47.64,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,They just keep outdoing me easily,\N without even caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人は 何でもない顔で\Nあっさり 上を行ってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.60,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Rena?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:49.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）玲奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.60,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ああ ごめん\N（玉来）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.56,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.35,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I hate that I'm no match for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\Nかなわないのは悔しいけど—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）主食\N牛乳にしちゃおうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:00.34,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,but I love Honoka regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとこれとは別で\Nほのかは大好きだし—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.28,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,She's a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい友達だと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.66,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも あの女は！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.83,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）にたー…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カズ君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.83,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.38,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I don't think I can ever\Ncome to terms with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:20.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）ぜんっぜん\N歩み寄れる気がしない！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.88,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why's she eating alone in the cafeteria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人で学食とか 何なの？\N“孤独です”アピール？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.34,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Trying to make herself look lonely?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）わあっ！\Nううっ ええ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.84,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Waiting for some dude to hit on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男から 声かけてもらえるのでも\N待ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玲奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.80,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.56,Main Dialogue,Both,0,0,0,,We're truly ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小野屋(おのや)･海崎）面目ない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）\Nいつまで続くんですか？ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.94,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,How long is this gonna go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小野屋）まだ３回目だよ\N（海崎）そうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.44,Main Dialogue,An,0,0,0,,It's only our third try!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.07,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.19,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Counting the real one, it's your fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）\N最初の本番入れたら ４回だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.74,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I dunno how you can take tests \Nfor a month straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく １か月も\Nテスト 受け続けられるよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.49,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Don't you even want to be free?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“そろそろ解放されたいな”とか\N思わないわけ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小野屋）思います！\N（海崎）切に！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.70,Main Dialogue,An,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Extremely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴールデンウィークに\N勉強会だなあ これじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.25,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll need to hold\Nstudy sessions through Golden Week...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）えっ\N（大神）“えっ”じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:56.75,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.50,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.88,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう やだ\N俺 教える自信 なくなってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.34,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I'm starting to lose confidence\Nin my teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.84,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Does Hishiro-san eat lunch alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんって\Nお昼 １人なのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,He's right. She's eating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）ほんとだ １人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.94,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:23.73,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,300)}I'm trying to take the first step \Ntoward not being a friendless loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\N友達ゼロの ぼっち女が—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とか 一歩\N踏み出してみたところなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.49,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんを ここに誘おう\N“一緒に食べよう”って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.78,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Let's invite her here to eat with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:33.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 勉強を教えるのを\N日代さんにも手伝ってもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:33.70,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,And we can have her help tutor you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて ぜいたくなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.04,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,How lucky is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シルバーピン ２人がかりとか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.96,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Two silver pins teaching you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小野屋･海崎）サーセン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.92,Main Dialogue,An,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.63,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I'll go ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んじゃ 俺\Nちょっと 声かけてくるね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… 大神 待った！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oga, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）うん？ なーに？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.26,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.67,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.14,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Oh, you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 新太(あらた)が行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:54.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば\Nちょっと 仲いいよね 日代さんと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.18,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Right. You two are on friendly terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Uh, no, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ いや そうじゃなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,We'd better not ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ 誘うの やめとこっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）ええ？ 何で？\Nちょうどいいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.40,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっちは １人だし\Nこっちは 人手が欲しいし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.07,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,She's alone, and we could use the help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）あっ いや\Nそれは分かるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）じゃあ 何でさ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.24,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Then why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）いやあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.33,Italics Dialogue,An,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:17.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小野屋）ああ… なるほどね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.04,Italics Dialogue,An,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.08,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.29,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,You're jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）しっとだ！\N（海崎）はっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.84,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,You don't want any other guys \Ngetting close to Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんに 自分以外の男子を\N近づけたくないんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）はあ!?\N（大神）大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.50,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.38,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,It'll be fine! Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配しなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違(ちげ)えよ バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.09,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That ain't it, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に恋愛話 振ろうなんざ\N10年 早(はえ)えわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:34.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,If you want to talk to me about love,\Ncome back in another ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大神のくせに！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 俺と杏(あん)が さっさと\N再試 合格すりゃいいんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:39.18,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,An and I just have to \Nbuckle down and pass, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Put Hishiro-san on hold for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんの件は いったん保留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）ふーん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.15,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yikes. He ain't buying that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\Nわあ… 信頼が地に落ちたね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ…\Nよく分かんないけど 分かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.07,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I don't get it, but whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.61,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで言うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう 再試 頑張るからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll do our best to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.04,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Might be none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\N気の回しすぎかもしれないけど—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.75,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,but I don't wanna see her and Kariu fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生と 泥沼化してほしくないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.96,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I want to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わりたいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり 私—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:09.46,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Am I really unapproachable?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっつきにくいんで\Nしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.01,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,But maybe I hurt Hishiro-san's chances a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）でも 日代さんには\N悪いことしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく 大神が誘おうとしたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.39,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Just when Oga thought to invite her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.22,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Now she's gonna stay alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ ぼっち継続だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.85,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Wait, why is this my problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つーか 何で 俺\Nこんなに考えてんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.02,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Let the kids be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキどもの問題だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）“日代さんって—”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:34.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro-san, don't you have \Nany friends to eat lunch with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“お昼を一緒に食べるような\N友達って いないの？”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.83,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.04,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Thought not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）やっぱりかあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.42,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Why are you even asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.01,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you I had no friends already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.42,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）うっ… やっべ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.43,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,A sticker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スタンプ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）\N何で 今 それ チョイスした!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.73,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why choose that one now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.69,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Is she emotionally unstable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,情緒不安定か！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.53,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.16,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,It feels like I might make a friend soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.70,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,I think I've been getting along\Nwith Kariu-san lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.00,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,What gave you that idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）なにゆえ そう思った!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:28.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 俺が気づかないとこで 何か\Nいい感じなことが起こってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:28.67,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Did something happen between them \Nwhen I wasn't looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:31.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや 昼の狩生の あの殺気
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:31.63,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,No, no. Kariu looked ready to kill at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に 日代さん\Nこれ 勘違いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.42,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,This is totally Hishiro-san \Nmisreading things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.26,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,How bad is she at observing\Nthose around her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ 周りが見えてないんだ\Nこの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前の覚えの悪さといい\N周囲に関心なさすぎなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.89,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Not to mention,\Nshe sucks at remembering names.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.35,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Maybe she doesn't care about other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.73,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Kids these days are so unsocial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドライだねえ 今どきの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:51.36,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,But damn... she really is totally alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:51.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし まいったなあ\Nガチぼっちか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）いるじゃん もう１人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.20,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I know someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.82,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaizaki Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.62,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,...who eats lunch alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お昼 ぼっちな人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）それは できませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.91,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:08.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でだよ？ どうせ\N夜明さんも ぼっちなんだし—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.41,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You're all alone, too, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,As a pair of loners,\Nthe two of you should get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんと ぼっち同士\N仲良くしてあげりゃいいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:15.30,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Considering you're trying to be nice, \Nyou sure have a rude way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）気遣ってくれる割に\N言葉が刺さりますねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ 僕も ぼっちだろうって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.72,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,What do you mean, I'm all alone anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:21.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は 仕事上\N１人を選んでるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.30,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I choose not to mingle for work reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:26.60,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I can't exactly stalk you \Nif I'm with Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんを\Nストーキングする時に—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代さんと 一緒にいるわけには\Nいかないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.85,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You were in the same class \Nas her last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）去年も 日代さんと\N同じクラスだったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.11,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,and you sit next to her. \NYou can at least eat—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,席も隣なんだしさ\N昼飯ぐらい 一緒に…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:34.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）できません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.03,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:39.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んだよ 冷てえな ドＳ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You cold-hearted sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）そこまで言うなら—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:43.28,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,If it's that important, \Nwhy not invite her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんが誘ってあげたら\Nいいじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.96,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I'm asking 'cause I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと できねえから\N頼んでるんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふっ どうしたんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:53.21,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,What's this? It sounds like you really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,随分 入れ込むじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無難に サラッと\N１年 過ぎれば—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.38,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,What happened to staying in\Nthe background all year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったんじゃないんでしたっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.10,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I think it's a good thing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）\Nいいと思いますよ そういうところ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.18,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,You're paying attention to those around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとに\Nよく周りを見てるんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.73,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,You don't just notice... \Nyou take action to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:11.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づけるだけでなく\N人のために行動できる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.32,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,I think it's one of your strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんの長所だなって思います
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）\Nでも どうなんでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.82,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,But don't you wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.95,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is getting rid of all the thorns\Nin someone's path
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:21.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石をどけた きれいな道を\N歩かせてあげることが—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はたして\N本人のためになるのかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.66,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,really what's best for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.33,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,While they're still young enough \Nto be allowed to trip and fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,転んでも許してもらえる\N若いうちに—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.75,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,it's important for them \Nto learn the pain of it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その痛みや 起き上がり方を\N学んでおくのも—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.29,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,and how to pick themselves up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大切かなって思いますがね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.26,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Every now and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）たまに—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:43.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）ふふーん\Nふふ ふふふっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:43.09,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,...you say something deep.\N It's kind of annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:43.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,深いこと言い出すの\N妙にムカつく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:49.10,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,So you think my attempts to help\Nwouldn't benefit them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 俺が こうして\N変に気を回すのは—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本人たちのためにならない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You don't recommend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おすすめしない… と
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:57.07,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,No, sorry. I just said what crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すみません つい 思ったことを\N言ってみちゃっただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:03.28,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,You can live your ReLIFE \Nany way you see fit, Kaizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎さんは\N海崎さんの思うままの—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:03.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リライフを過ごしていただければ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.08,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the line, my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）いつの間にか\N俺の生活の中心が—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.29,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,...my thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:15.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の頭の中が あいつらで\Nいっぱいになっていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.79,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,...began to revolve around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.05,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't it a shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって もったいねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくなら いい学生生活を\N送ってほしいなって思うじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:27.39,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I just want them all to enjoy \Nthe time they're having at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.85,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm thinking like an old man \Nprone to lectures...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:31.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説教くさいオヤジみてえな\N考え方かもしんねえけど—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前のように\N友達に会える毎日なんて—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:35.35,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,But seeing your friends every day \Nlike it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.32,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,...is something you lose\N when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:39.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大人になったら\Nなくなってしまうのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.49,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Fight with all your might.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夜明）\Nあがいてください 精いっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思春期の学生たちと一緒に—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:52.41,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,With those young kids, give your\Nmind and heart a solid workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頭だけじゃなく\N心を いっぱい動かして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:58.21,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Let your heart, which had dried up\N and gotten stiff, beat once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乾いて固まっていた心が—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,揺らぎ始めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,May 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.64,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,May, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）５月か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.85,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I've been at this ReLIFE thing\Na whole month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リライフ生活も １か月\N終わっちゃったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.64,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Not sure if it went by in a flash\Nor lasted forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長かったような 早かったような
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.73,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）新太\N（海崎）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 今日 委員会あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I've got a committee meeting, so here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:21.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい これ\N再試の やり直しプリント
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.40,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,A handout for your make-up retest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 大神がいないなら\N今日は 居残り勉強 なしなのかと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,With you gone, I figured \Nwe wouldn't be studying today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.87,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you'd do your best?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“頑張る”って言ったよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）はい… ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I did. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:38.17,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,You know there's a study room at\N the end of the second floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）２階の突き当たりに\N自習室あるの 知ってるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと解いてから帰ること
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.17,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Be sure to solve that before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.17,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カズ君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行きますよ 委員会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.59,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Let's go to the committee meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.59,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:48.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）ああ ごめん 日代さん\N行こっか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.76,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:49.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.48,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Oh... Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）狩生さん\Nまた 目が合った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.10,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Our eyes met again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\Nほのかー！ 部活 行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.98,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Honoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.36,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Let's go to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）\N日代さん？ 行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.74,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,C'mon, Hishiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）\Nはっ… ああ… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.41,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,U-Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:22.13,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Does she smile at Oga\Nthe way she smiles at Kaizaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:17.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）大神にも—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海崎に見せてたような顔で\N笑ってるんだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.48,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,We're out of balls. Better pick 'em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）ボール なくなっちゃった\N拾おうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.18,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.90,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朝地(あさじ)）あっ いた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.61,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,See? I told you they'd still be at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほらね\Nやっぱり まだ やってた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（犬飼(いぬかい)）帰るぞ タマ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.94,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.94,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ あれ？ もう そんな時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.53,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Is it that late?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.99,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Sorry, I totally lost track of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん\Nすっかり 時間忘れちゃってた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,着替えておいでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.87,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも まだ ボール…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.37,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,But the balls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）いいよ\Nあたし まだ残るし—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.33,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'm not leaving yet, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.41,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You need to catch your train, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電車の時間があるんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）うん ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.92,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アキちゃん ノブちゃん 待ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.88,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Aki-chan, Nobu-chan, wait right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.88,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,I'll go get changed in a jiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐ 着替えてくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.68,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朝地）ごめんね 狩生さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも 遅くまで タマちゃんに\N付き合ってもらっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.76,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,Tama-chan always makes you \Nstay late with her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.52,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,But, thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:17.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかげで タマちゃん\N昔に比べて すごく部活が楽しそう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:17.43,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she seems to be enjoying \Npractice a lot more than she used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.15,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Nah. I'm the one making her stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に… 付き合ってもらってるのは\N私のほうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちこそ 毎日 すごいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.15,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,You're doing more for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな時間まで待って\N一緒に帰るなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.65,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Waiting this late to go home with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.57,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,If we let Tama-chan ride a train alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タマちゃんを\N１人で電車に乗せると—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.45,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,who knows where she'd end up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこ行っちゃうか 分かんなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.39,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0,0,0,,Our parents insist we have to \Nlook after her and bring her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“お前らが ちゃんと面倒見て\N連れて帰れ”って—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親同士が うるせえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.04,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.17,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.34,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0,0,0,,No prob.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）\Nはあ… お待たせ 帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.01,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朝地）はーい\N（犬飼）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:49.51,Main Dialogue,Both,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:49.97,Main Dialogue,Both,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ ごめん 玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.26,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry, Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと 部室と体育館の\N戸締まりしたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.05,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,When you're done,\Nlock up the clubroom and gym
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鍵を 職員室にお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.89,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,and return the key to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.97,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉来）じゃあね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.48,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）いいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.74,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.16,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Spending every day with\Nnice childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）優しい幼なじみと\N毎日 一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.42,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Kariu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）狩生… さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ テスト 同じ点じゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.96,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Oh, we got the same scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１学期 委員長\N一緒に頑張ろうな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.47,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Let's work hard together as\Nthe class reps for first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.47,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:41.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）１年の１学期\Nクラス委員長になって—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.35,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I was the Class 1 rep \Nthe first term of my first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.02,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But I didn't come first the next two terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも ２学期と３学期は\N１位になれなくて—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.98,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I hated that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.69,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,so I made sure I had\Nthe silver pin for all of last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,去年は ずっと シルバーピン
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大神）狩生！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.36,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,委員会 行こ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.95,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Committee time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.16,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.16,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,For an entire year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）１年間 ずっと\Nシルバー キープしてたのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.00,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I never let go of the silver pin, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）何で…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.55,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.06,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why always me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）何で 私ばっかり…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.44,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why can't I do anything right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で 何もうまくいかないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… 嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.90,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.28,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I can't stand being like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな自分 カッコ悪い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.78,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！ まだ 時々 痛むなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,It still hurts sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Is this what it means to age?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが 年か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）こんな時間に\Nまだ 生徒がいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:00.30,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,There are still students around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.14,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.48,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'm here to return the gym key.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体育館の鍵を返しに来ました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）日代？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.36,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Hishiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.49,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）失礼しました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.75,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）これ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代のかばん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.54,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...is Hishiro's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.18,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,The silver pin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）シルバーピン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.68,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Proof that you're number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:42.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１位の証
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:43.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張った証
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.93,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Proof that you worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも あたしにとっては\Nステータスだけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.48,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,But for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.69,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,it wasn't just the status.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしにとって—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.44,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.57,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.32,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,...proof that I deserved to be with Oga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大神の隣にいられる証でも\Nあったのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:06.33,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,She got everything without looking\Nlike she put in any effort at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の努力もしてないような\N涼しい顔で—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もかも手に入れて！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しぐらい 困ればいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.29,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,She deserves some trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.29,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,It'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 バレやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.50,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I won't get caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平然と 学校を出て\N駅のトイレにでも置いて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.71,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I'll just walk casually out of school\Nand ditch it at the station bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,You're leaving now, Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生 今 帰り？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海… 崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.10,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Kaizaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.14,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:30.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で こんな時間に？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh, studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 居残りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自習室 使ってたんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.40,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I was using the study room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.07,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,The teacher said to lock up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:38.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰る時は 鍵かけて\N職員室まで返しに来いって—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,and bring the key by the \Nstaff room when I was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:39.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生に言われて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,How about you? Just finished practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生は 部活帰りか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.95,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）どうした？\N（狩生）えっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.79,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… あたしも\N体育館の鍵を返してきたとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I just returned the gym key, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）ああ そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.00,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）来ないで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 鍵のしまい場所が\N分かんなくてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I don't know where to put the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.43,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I can't stop to chat here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）こんな所で\N足止め食ってる場合じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you come with and show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）悪いんだけど 一緒に来て\N教えてくんねえかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.64,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,If I waste too much time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）\Nあんまり のんびりしてたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日代が 職員室から出てきちゃう！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.77,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Hishiro will leave the staff room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.19,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごっ ごめん\Nあたし もう 帰んなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.65,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I've gotta get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.52,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you ask a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いんだけど\N先生に聞いてくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）そっか\N気いつけて帰れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.23,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,All right. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で かばん ２つ持ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.16,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Why do you have two bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（狩生）はっ？ 別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.54,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.41,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通でしょ？ 部活の着替えとか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.38,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,I mean, for my practice clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.67,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I recognize that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:42.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 見覚えあるんだけど\Nその緑色の
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,The green one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ 日代さんのじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro-san's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.48,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.32,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hey, Kariu! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 狩生 待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）待てって！\N（狩生）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.32,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやあっ 放してよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.73,Main Dialogue,Rena,0,0,0,,No! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:05.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狩生！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）失礼しました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.34,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.17,Black Signs 1,,0,0,0,,Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.56,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？ かばんが…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:31.81,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:34.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（日代）というか 今\N何か ものすごい音が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.44,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.87,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,Fall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:22.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:39.97,Next Episode,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（海崎）俺は 運動神経は\N悪いほうじゃないし—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:28.46,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't bad at sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二浪はしたけど 勉強が\Nできないというわけでもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:31.83,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and despite taking two years to get into \Ncollege, I wasn't bad at studying, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大学院まで行って\N就職先も 無事 決まったし—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.30,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to grad school
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.31,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and managed to land a job all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.97,Next Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)}Overlap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:38.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,充実した社会人ライフが\N待っていると思ってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.90,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I had a fulfilling\Nadult life waiting for me.
